name: The Majestic Liong Bulan
description:
I created this illustration as a tribute to my daily booze,
the True Bogorian Black Coffee; Liong Bulan.
When a majestic Dragon kiss the glorious everlasting Moon.

summoning through day and night, bright and twilight.. 
our highest nocturnal majesty..
with or without sweet sugar, sworn to black we’ll always be..

 I can’t live without you, o my dearest Liong Bulan..
